title: Greg Plitt SiteRip
description:
The site rip is not FULL, but almost complete. I don't think that the site managers should continue to make money from the name and the knowledge of Greg Plitt!

Sadly during the making and starting the seeding of this torrent I lost the whole folder with all the files. I was able to recover some of them, but some got broken. Why ? - Every file is made by manually downloading and joining each of download *.ts file parts(~2MBs each). During the recovery process some of the files got replaced by the pieces which were part of other files.


TL;DR: Please note that the files having the %_fixed% in their file names are BROKEN!
